author: Disney
description:
Join us in celebrating Amanda's incredible journey with Make-A-Wish® and Disney! When Amanda was 8 years old, she had the chance to meet the creators of Phineas & Ferb, Dan and Swampy, thanks to Make-A-Wish and Disney. Now, years later, Amanda gets to reunite with them for Disney's Week of Wishes.

Disney is proud to be the world’s largest wish granter for Make-A-Wish®. A Disney wish is granted every hour of every day – and we are honored that wish kids choose Disney for their most heartfelt wish. Nearly 45 years ago, the first official wish was granted at Disneyland. Since then, Disney has worked with Make-A-Wish® to grant wishes and create happiness and joy for kids and families when it’s needed most, in ways that only Disney can.

To learn how you can become a WishMaker for Make-A-Wish, visit wish.org/Disney
